ZH: 我的姓氏是王。
EN: My family name is Wang.

ZH: 我不知道他的姓氏。
EN: I don't know his last name.

ZH: 请告诉我你的全名，包括姓氏。
EN: Please tell me your full name, including your last name.

ZH: 她的姓氏很特别。
EN: Her last name is very unique.

ZH: 姓氏在中国文化中非常重要。
EN: Last names are very important in Chinese culture.

ZH: 我喜欢她的姓氏，因为很有音乐感。
EN: I like her last name because it sounds musical.

ZH: 姓氏是家族的象征。
EN: Last names symbolize the family.

ZH: 他的姓氏和我很相似。
EN: His last name is very similar to mine.

ZH: 对于很多外国人来说，中文姓氏很难发音。
EN: For many foreigners, Chinese last names are difficult to pronounce.

ZH: 姓氏通常代代相传。
EN: Last names are usually passed down from generation to generation.

ZH: 她的姓氏意味着“大地之王”。
EN: Her last name means "king of the earth".

ZH: 关于一个人的姓氏，可以了解很多有关他们家族的信息。
EN: You can learn a lot about a person's family from their last name.

ZH: 很多人在婚后会改变姓氏。
EN: Many people change their last name after marriage.

ZH: 姓氏的意义在不同的文化中有所不同。
EN: The significance of last names varies in different cultures.

ZH: 他们的姓氏是家族的标志。
EN: Their last name is the symbol of their family.

ZH: 许多姓氏起源于地理名称。
EN: Many last names originated from geographical names.

ZH: 姓氏还可以反映一个人的职业。
EN: Last names can also reflect a person's occupation.

ZH: 你的姓氏能够影响你在社会中的地位。
EN: Your last name can influence your social status.

ZH: 她非常自豪自己的姓氏。
EN: She takes great pride in her last name.

ZH: 我没有听说过这个姓氏。
EN: I haven't heard of this last name before.
